<div id="wrap">
  <h1>Debate.me!</h1>
  <p>
    Debate.me is a website that allows you to have debates
    that where each point can be individually supported, refuted,
    and sourced. If a proposition is blue, then it has lots of
    support. If it is red, it doesn't have much support.
  </p>
  <p>
    To start debating, choose one of the debates below, or create a new debate.
  </p>
  
  <b>Ongoing debates:</b>
  <table>
    <% @debates.find_all{|debate| debate.debate == nil}.each do |debate| %>
    <tr>
      <td <%= debate.generate_style %> ><%= link_to debate.proposition, debate %></td>
    </tr>
    <% end %>
  </table>

  <br />

  <%= link_to 'New Debate', new_debate_path %>
</div>
